Edith Haldeman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edith_Haldeman 0 Edith Haldeman (April 17, 1905 – October 1984) was an American child actress of the early silent film era. She appeared in 36 films between 1909 and 1916. Edith_Haldeman ( April_17_,_1905 – October_1984 ) was an_American_child_actress of the_early_silent_film_era .
